Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait compared to the duration of Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and the subsequent occurrence of Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait in variants that end with Completed + Resolved versus those that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait when it appears before Completed + In Call versus when it appears before Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Wait in cases that contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + In Call across all variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time until Accepted + Wait is performed after Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Resolved in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call, contrasted with those that do
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (e.g., top 5 by frequency) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
